fields.saying: I have never met a successful excuse maker.
fields.author: Nav-Vii

fields.saying: I only start counting when it starts hurting because they're the only ones that count.
fields.author: Muhammed Ali

fields.saying: Its hard to beat a person who never gives up.
fields.author: Babe Ruth

fields.saying: Strength does not come from physical capacity. It comes from an indomitable will.
fields.author: Gandhi

fields.saying: I've failed over and over and over again in my life. And that is why I succeed.
fields.author: Michael Jordan

fields.saying: No one ever drowned in sweat.
fields.author: Lou Holtz

fields.saying: Strong is what happens when you run out of weak.
fields.author: Nicole Nichols

fields.saying: A one-hour workout is 4% of your day. No excuses.
fields.author: Geoff Bagshaw

fields.saying: Forget the 'no' in your head and listen to the 'yes' in your body.
fields.author: Paul Katami

fields.saying: When you think about quitting, think about why you started.
fields.author: Anonymous

fields.saying: I saw a woman wearing a sweatshirt with 'Guess' on it. I said, 'Thyroid problem?'
fields.author: Arnold Schwarzenegger

fields.saying: Our growing softness, our increasing lack of physical fitness, is a menace to our security.
fields.author: John F. Kennedy

fields.saying: Pain makes me grow. Growing is what I want. Therefore, for me pain is pleasure.
fields.author: Arnold Schwarzenegger

fields.saying: Sweat is weakness leaving the body.
fields.author: Anonymous

fields.saying: Real g's move in silence like lasagna.
fields.author: Lil Wayne

fields.saying: I don't know, man. I guess I'm gonna fade into Bolivian.
fields.author: Mike Tyson

fields.saying: My image is a strategic hot mess.
fields.author: Miley Cyrus

fields.saying: I'm addicted to perfection.
fields.author: Mike Tyson

fields.saying: These dudes are trying to crucify me and I'm like 'Bro, do you even lift?'
fields.author: Jesus of Nazareth

fields.saying: Hoes on my dick cuz I look like Jesus.
fields.author: Lil B

fields.saying: I don't workout my legs cause then I can't fit into skinny jeans, I don't workout my back cause I can't see it.
fields.author: Dom Mazzetti

fields.saying: If a brick didn't know how to sit on walls no mo' ... What would you ask it?
fields.author: The ODB

fields.saying: Greatness is what we on the brink of
fields.author: Nicki Minaj
